Для работы с vue, необходимо создать корневой проект, аналогично django:
1. sudo npm install -g @vue/cli
2. vue create `project name`
3. ~In directory, you should install axios for backend and bulma for scss~ 
    npm install axios
    npm install bulma
4. To start project, run command: npm run serve

In the core project we have:
1. views - include different pages
2. store - contain global statement of the whole project
3. router - is the same as url for django
4. components - large or small re-usable part of codes
5. assets - contain images or the same thing that needs website
